Вакансія від 18 березня 2020
Sales manager (English, Hindu, Arabic, call-center)
12 000 грн · Rate + %
MonsterLeads CPA
Маркетинг, реклама, PR;
50–250 співробітників
Київ
Повна зайнятість, неповна зайнятість, готові взяти студента.
Опис вакансії
Modern and fast growing company «Upsale.Me» is looking for ambitious English speaking sales-manager. «Upsale.Me» — is an International outsourcing call-center.We offer:
High salary (rate + bonuses)
Bonuses due to the results of successful work
Comfortable office near city center
Career prospects
Opportunities for self-development
Convenient work schedule due to your wishes
Corporate sales trannings
Corporate holidays and events
Friendly team
Main requirements:
Fluent in English
Knowledge of English-Arabic, English-Hindu, would be an advantage
Sociability and good communication skills
Experience in active sales or work in the call-center would be an advantage but is not necessarily
Desire to work for better results
Open-minded and talkative personality
Ability to plan your schedule
Duties:
Confirming orders that were placed by customers in internet
Knowledge of all products and services of the company (after education)
Join our team now and start to earn your money in efficient and friendly company!
